  "widgets": [
    {
      "definition": {
        "type": "note",
        "content": "# Smart Hospital Demo\n### Real-time Device Observability Command Center\n\nMonitoring **Medical IoT** \u00b7 **Network Infrastructure** \u00b7 **Environmental Sensors** \u00b7 **Asset Tracking**\n\nAll telemetry streamed via OpenTelemetry \u2192 Datadog",
